data.description: Discover modern comfort in this exquisite duplex, nestled in a serene neighborhood. Each unit features two bedrooms and one bathroom, seamlessly blending functionality with style. The main level boasts sleek design and updates, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The upper level unit offers tasteful upgrades for a refined living experience. Enjoy ample storage in the full basement, a shared fenced-in backyard, and private parking. With a charming brick exterior and low maintenance, this duplex is both a cozy sanctuary and an investment opportunity. Experience the pinnacle of comfort and sophistication - schedule your viewing today!
